{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FormData.getAll()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/FormData\"><code>FormData()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\"><code>append()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/delete\"><code>delete()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/entries\"><code>entries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><em><code>getAll()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/has\"><code>has()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/keys\"><code>keys()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>set()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/values\"><code>values()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for XMLHttpRequest</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ProgressEvent\"><code>ProgressEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>XMLHttpRequestUpload</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>getAll()</strong></code>方法会返回该 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a> 对象指定 key 的所有值。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>注意：</strong>&nbsp;该方法在&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a>&nbsp;中可用。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"append()_parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"name\"><code>name</code></dt>\n <dd>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a> 表示要检索的 key 名称。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回","title":"返回","isH3":true,"content":"<p>一个 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormDataEntryValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 数组。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列代码会先创建一个空的&nbsp;<code>FormData</code>&nbsp;对象：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> formData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FormData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\"><code>FormData.append</code></a> 添加两个&nbsp;<code>username 的值：</code></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'username'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Chris'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nformData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'username'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Bob'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>下列&nbsp;<code>getAll()</code>&nbsp;方法会返回一个数组，包含了所有&nbsp;<code>username</code> 的值：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'username'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Returns [\"Chris\", \"Bob\"]</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-formdata-getall","title":"XMLHttpRequest Standard"}],"query":"api.FormData.getAll"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.FormData.getAll","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHTTPRequest</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\">使用 XMLHttpRequest</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/Using_FormData_Objects\">使用 FormData 对象</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"getAll()方法会返回该 FormData 对象指定 key 的所有值。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/formdata/getall","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/formdata/getall/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData","title":"FormData"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll","title":"FormData.getAll()"}],"pageTitle":"FormData.getAll() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}